posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 713 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Zócalo offers a luxury experience like no other, a one-of-a-kind apartment community rooted in celebration, culture, and the artisan spirit.', 'From our artist-in-residence program to touch points of heritage found throughout the multimillion dollar community renovation, Zócalo is a great place to live with unmatched on-site personal service.', 'We offer brand-new stylish kitchens and baths, a welcoming clubhouse, and gorgeous landscaping.', 'Residents benefit from close proximity to employment centers, downtown Houston, and the surrounding areas full of shopping, dining, and entertainment.', 'We have specially designed Zócalo with convenient app-based concierge services to complete your modern lifestyle.', 'Find your center — find your home — and discover what a true sense of community is all about at Zócalo.', 'Features:', 'Luxury Apartments, Brand New Kitchens, Brand New Baths, Private Patios*, Tech-savvy Features Like USB Outlets, Upscale Features, Granite Countertops, Brand-new Black Appliances, Built-in Microwave, Washer And Dryer*, Two-tone Cabinets, Vinyl Faux Wood Floors', '*In select apartments only', 'Community Amenities:', '24-hour Emergency Maintenance, Valet Trash Pickup, Package Lockers, Sparkling Pool, Pet Friendly, Group Exercise Classes, Artist-in-residence Program, Coffeehouse, Resident App & Portal, Resort-like Ambiance, Party Room, Concierge Services, Dedicated Yoga Studio, On-site Gym, Laundry Center', 'Want more information on this unit?', 'See link (below):', '<URL>', 'j9K93fLNNd4f']
